{"rightSidebarLinks":[{"id":"rule","title":"rule","subLink":null},{"id":"whentouse","title":"When to use","subLink":[]},{"id":"basicrulevalidation","title":"Basic rule Validation","subLink":[]},{"id":"ruleconfig","title":"RuleConfig","subLink":[{"title":"customRules","id":"customrules","thirdLevelLink":[]},{"title":"conditionalExpression","id":"conditionalexpression","thirdLevelLink":[]}]},{"id":"completeruleexample","title":"Complete rule Example","subLink":[]},{"id":"dynamicruleexample","title":"Dynamic rule Example","subLink":[]}],"title":"rule","description":"Rule validation decorator will allow the user to set custom rules on a particular field.","validatorType":"template-driven","validationTypeTitle":"Template Driven","type":"","category":"","linkTitle":"","tabArray":{"complete":[],"dynamic":[]},"innerHtml":null,"htmlContent":"<div class='row page-section' id= 'whentouse'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2 class='showHideElement' >When to use<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='///template-driven#whentouse'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Suppose you want to create a Address Info form, which contains fields like Zipcode, City, Country and you want the user to enter value based upon your custom rules. Here depending upon the requirement, these scenarios may arise..</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n  <li>Allow Zipcode which is based on the custom rules.</li>\r\n  <li>Apply rule validation on City field based on matched condition in the form, like if the Zipcode is '10001', then the zipCode must be a according to the rule (Used as a function).</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Let's see how rule decorator fulfil the need.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'basicrulevalidation'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Basic rule Validation<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='///template-driven#basicrulevalidation'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >First we need to create a Address Model and define a property of zipCode in the model to achieve the functional need of point 1.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"rule-add-model\"></div> \r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Now, we need to create a <span class='highlighted'>FormGroup</span> in the component. To achieve this we need to add <span class='highlighted'>RxFormBuilder</span>. The <span class='highlighted'>RxFormBuilder</span> is an injectable service that is provided with the <span class='highlighted'>RxReactiveFormsModule</span>. Inject this dependency by adding it to the component constructor.</p>\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Here we have covered Add and Edit form operations.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'ruleconfig'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2 class='showHideElement' >RuleConfig<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='///template-driven#ruleconfig'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'customrules'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>customRules<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='///template-driven#customrules'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'conditionalexpression'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>conditionalExpression<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='///template-driven#conditionalexpression'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'completeruleexample'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Complete rule Example<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='///template-driven#completeruleexample'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div component=\"app-tabs\" key=\"complete\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'dynamicruleexample'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Dynamic rule Example<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='///template-driven#dynamicruleexample'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div component=\"app-tabs\" key=\"dynamic\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n"}